{"tid":1467552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有網站自動備份疑似公安輔警資料檔","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:53:50.000Z","uid":180575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f133bc6e0312d2a0ec5fbbdf939c0192807e5aad","tid":1467552,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"以下為WayBack Machine使用教學<br />\n教大家如何搜尋互聯網上已被刪的檔案<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<br />\nGoogle搜尋「徐锦炀 公安」，共有三個大陸網站檔案<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/010130_091134ef0dfbc730031f29d4cac753d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F010130_091134ef0dfbc730031f29d4cac753d2.png&h=f88908cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個檔案仍在（預計將會被刪除）<br />\n<a href=\"http://gd.offcn.com/dl/2018/0925/20180925030428312.xls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgd.offcn.com%2Fdl%2F2018%2F0925%2F20180925030428312.xls&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=89b15450\" target=\"_blank\">http://gd.offcn.com/dl/2018/0925/20180925030428312.xls</a><br />\n<br />\n有兩個檔案已被刪<br />\n但其中一個檔案<br />\nWayBack Machine網站仍有自動backup檔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/010232_fe3426914736c1c25881e7fb79ce3da9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F010232_fe3426914736c1c25881e7fb79ce3da9.png&h=d2ecb307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190813121539/http://ga.sz.gov.cn/ZWGK/QT/GSGG/201810/P020181011659869054827.xlsx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20190813121539%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fga.sz.gov.cn%2FZWGK%2FQT%2FGSGG%2F201810%2FP020181011659869054827.xlsx&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=838deadc\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20190813121539/http://ga.sz.gov.cn/ZWGK/QT/GSGG/201810/P020181011659869054827.xlsx</a><br />\n<br />\nWayBack Machine網站是很實用的工具<br />\n以上教學所有曾下載的檔案請自行刪除"},{"pid":"eeb74784ea345296330aabdfa244a2ff5a8b960f","tid":1467552,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"push"}]}